c: 5
v: 5
t: "Hodie totus bonus food factus lawful vos. food people scripture est lawful pro vos. Alias vos maritus pudica femina believers alias prout pudica femina followers proximus scripture provisus vos pay them their due dos. Vos maintain chastity non committing adultery, nor taking secret lovers! Anyone rejects faith totus his work est in vain Hereafter he est losers"